name: dynast admin panel
author: goniusman

sections.description:
hello guy, how are you? i think you are well. this is a awesome plugin for little customization of your website. my students often ask to create a custom contact without many code like contact form 7. it’s simple contact form

There are some input filed in my this plugin if you would like to increase input filed just contact me i will customize your theme from skratch.

If you run a WordPress website, you should absolutely use “dynast-admin-panel” to lead the website properly, in this plugin you will get a contact form and more feature.

for them admin identity show on the frontend site by widget that i already have been create and a aweosme css editor and so on.

Special Features

  1. contact form
  2. widget for admin identity.
  3. css editor.
  4. theme furntionality and so on.
sections.installation:
1. Upload the entire bbpress-admin-bar-addition folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
  3. Look at your admin bar and enjoy using the new links there…
  4. Go and manage your dynast admin panel…
sections.faq:
Does this plugin work with newest WP version and also older versions?

Yes, this plugin works really fine with WordPress 3.3!
It also works great with WP 3.2 – and also should with WP 3.1 – but we only tested extensively with WP 3.3 and 3.2. So you always should run the latest WordPress version for a lot of reasons.

How are new resources being added to the admin bar?

user friendly.
